  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1118830">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1118830/" class="title-link">如果只可以选择一本台湾出版的书……</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1118830"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1403165/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1403165/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">echo</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-02-02"
      class="main-meta">2007-02-02 06:52:20</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1118830_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      李爽，估计我的同龄人都不知道她是谁。我也是冲着“作者”里的阿城借的这本竖排本《爽》，另一人当然就是李爽。李爽，女，生于1957年，参加过1979年的“星星画会”（我理解这是个非政府组织的、蛮前卫蛮地下的艺术展），后因与法国外交官恋爱被捕，劳教两年，后经未婚夫在...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1118830/#comments">(2回应)</a>
